    " autocmd WinEnter * set cul   | set colorcolumn=80
    " autocmd WinLeave * set nocul | set colorcolumn=0
" augroup END

" Less aggressive highlighting of spelling errors
hi SpellBad cterm=undercurl ctermbg=052

